Distribution. Mexico , Bahamas , Cuba , Belize , Haiti , Dominican Republic , Puerto Rico , Guatemala , Honduras , Nicaragua , Costa Rica , Panama , Venezuela , Guyana , Surinam , Brazil ( Ceará , Paraíba , Pernambuco , Bahia , Trindade Island, Cabo Frio, São Paulo), Canary Islands, Cape Verde ( Verrill, 1915 ; Caso, 1944 ; Tommasi, 1958 ; Brito, 1960 ; 1962 ; 1968 ; Walenkamp, 1976 ; Clark & Downey, 1992 ;
Hendler et al . 1995
; Guzman & Guevara, 2002 ;
